      "front": "What is a Data Quality Initiative?",
      "back": "A Data Quality Initiative is a process or program aimed at improving the accuracy, completeness, and consistency of data across an organization."
    },
    {
      "front": "What is the main goal of a Data Quality Initiative?",
      "back": "The main goal of a Data Quality Initiative is to ensure that the data is accurate, reliable, and consistent, which is critical for making informed business decisions."
